        "e_zh": "在标准式 $A \\times 10^n$ 中，$1 \\le A < 10$。只有 7.2 符合这个条件。此外，$n$ 必须是整数。"
      },
      {
        "q": "What is $(6 \\times 10^8) \\div (3 \\times 10^2)$?",
        "q_zh": "$(6 \\times 10^8) \\div (3 \\times 10^2)$ 是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$2 \\times 10^4$",
          "$2 \\times 10^6$",
          "$18 \\times 10^{10}$",
          "$2 \\times 10^{10}$"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "$6 \\div 3 = 2$ and $10^8 \\div 10^2 = 10^{8-2} = 10^6$. Result is $2 \\times 10^6$.",
        "e_zh": "$6 \\div 3 = 2$ 且 $10^8 \\div 10^2 = 10^{8-2} = 10^6$。结果是 $2 \\times 10^6$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-E1.10-01",
    "section": "1.10",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Estimation",
    "title_zh": "估算",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "To estimate the value of a complex calculation, round every number to **One Significant Figure** before performing the operations.",
      "zh": "要估算复杂计算的值，请在进行运算前将每个数字舍入到**一位有效数字**。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-estimate-calc",
        "label": "Estimate the value of an expression",
        "label_zh": "估算表达式的值",
        "description": "Use 1 sf rounding to provide an approximate answer.",
        "description_zh": "使用 1 位有效数字舍入法提供近似答案。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-estimate-calc",
        "question": "Estimate the value of $\\frac{41.3 \\times 19.8}{0.49}$",
        "question_zh": "估算 $\\frac{41.3 \\times 19.8}{0.49}$ 的值",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Round each number to 1 sf: $41.3 \\to 40$; $19.8 \\to 20$; $0.49 \\to 0.5$.\n**Step 2:** Substitute: $\\frac{40 \\times 20}{0.5}$.\n**Step 3:** Calculate: $\\frac{800}{0.5} = 1600$.\n\n**Answer:** 1600",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 将每个数字舍入到 1 位有效数字：$41.3 \\to 40$；$19.8 \\to 20$；$0.49 \\to 0.5$。\n**步骤2：** 代入：$\\frac{40 \\times 20}{0.5}$。\n**步骤3：** 计算：$\\frac{800}{0.5} = 1600$。\n\n**答案：** 1600",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1F/June/2018"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-estimate-calc",
        "question": "Estimate the value of $\\sqrt{98.5 \\times 4.1^2}$",
        "question_zh": "估算 $\\sqrt{98.5 \\times 4.1^2}$ 的值",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Round to 1 sf: $98.5 \\to 100$; $4.1 \\to 4$.\n**Step 2:** Substitute: $\\sqrt{100 \\times 4^2}$.\n**Step 3:** Calculate: $\\sqrt{100 \\times 16} = \\sqrt{1600} = 40$.\n\n**Answer:** 40",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 舍入到 1 位有效数字：$98.5 \\to 100$；$4.1 \\to 4$。\n**步骤2：** 代入：$\\sqrt{100 \\times 4^2}$。\n**步骤3：** 计算：$\\sqrt{100 \\times 16} = \\sqrt{1600} = 40$。\n\n**答案：** 40",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2F/Jan/2021"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
